OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,FTwenty-five years after the Armed
OL,8,FForces so-called 'gay ban' was lifted,
OL,9,FBritish LGBTQ+ military veterans have
OL,10,Fshared their experiences in a new
OL,11,Fcomic strip. They spoke to ITV News
OL,12,FReporter Martha Fairlie
OL,14,FSteve Purves was dishonourably
OL,15,Fdischarged from the Air Force in 1985,
OL,16,Fwhen he was found to be in a
OL,17,Frelationship with a man.
