OL,7,FCourt marshalled and dismissed with
OL,8,Fdisgrace, he lost all his financial
OL,9,Fbenefits and served six months in
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,F"I was so angry about it all because I
OL,13,Fdidn't feel it should be happening,"
OL,14,Fhe told ITV News. "I kept thinking
OL,15,Fsomeone would intervene and quash it,
OL,16,Fbut they never did.
OL,18,F"It took a long time to come to terms
OL,19,Fwith what had happened and to face it.
OL,20,FYears and years and years and years
OL,21,Ffor me."
