OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,FNow, Steve's story, among other LGBTQ+
OL,8,Fveterans', is being told in a new
OL,9,Fanthology comic, Coming Home, from
OL,10,Fcharity Re-Live.
OL,12,FThis month's edition focuses on the
OL,13,Fenduring impact of the UK military's
OL,14,F'gay ban' on veterans' mental health,
OL,15,Fmarking the 25th anniversary of the
OL,16,Flifting of the ban.
