OL,3,C'They said I was a danger': LGBTQ+
OL,4,Cveterans speak out 25 years after 'gay
OL,5,Cban'
OL,7,FUntil 2000, homosexuality was banned
OL,8,Fin the Armed Forces. Under the ban,
OL,9,Fthousands of LGBTQ+ service personnel
OL,10,Fwere subjected to surveillance and
OL,11,Finterrogation and faced court
OL,12,Fmartials, dismissals for conduct
OL,13,Funbecoming and even imprisonment.
OL,15,FIt wasn't until July 2023 that the
OL,16,Fthen Prime Minister Rishi Sunak
OL,17,Fapologised to the hundreds of veterans
OL,18,Fwho were persecuted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
