OL,7,FThe stories in Coming Home are co-
OL,8,Fcreated with each veteran and a
OL,9,Fprofessional cartoonist to develop
OL,10,Ftheir own narrative.
OL,12,FSteve describes the process of making
OL,13,Fthe comic as thrilling and says the
OL,14,Ffinished product helps him to tell
OL,15,Fothers about his experience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
