OL,7,F"I would go to work and be the person
OL,8,Fthat everybody expected me to be and
OL,9,Fdo this 'Top Gun', amazing job. But
OL,10,FI'd go home, lock the doors, close the
OL,11,Fcurtains and then I would relax and
OL,12,Fjust be myself, be Caroline."
OL,14,FLieutenant Caroline Paige describes
OL,15,Fthe huge pressure she felt to hide who
OL,16,Fshe was while serving in the Armed
OL,17,FForces
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
