OL,7,F"So even up until the point of 2000
OL,8,Fwhen the band was lifted, that three
OL,9,Fyear period of leaving the military
OL,10,Fand that band being lifted, I
OL,11,Fliterally couldn't say anything. So I
OL,12,Fnever lived my life authentically then
OL,13,Fbecause I was so worried that if I'd
OL,14,Fsaid or admitted I was gay, I could
OL,15,Fstill be in trouble. I thought I could
OL,16,Fbe jailed."
OL,18,F'I never lived my life authentically
OL,19,Fthen because I was so worried I would
OL,20,Fbe in trouble,' says Kelly Holmes
