OL,7,F"I think the themes and the stories
OL,8,Fthat are told in this edition have
OL,9,Flinks to universal themes around
OL,10,Fidentity and belonging, links to
OL,11,Fisolation and loneliness, and the
OL,12,Fimpact on our mental health and
OL,13,Fwellbeing."
OL,15,FComing Home Comic has been co-created
OL,16,Fby Arts in Health charity Re-Live, in
OL,17,Fpartnership with Fighting With Pride,
OL,18,Fthe LGBTQ+ military veterans charity.
